        <title>PVE虚拟机UEFI启动时跳转到系统安装界面</title>
        <link>http://localhost:1313/p/388/</link>
        <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>http://localhost:1313/p/388/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="http://localhost:1313/p/388/20250507022533.jpg" alt="Featured image of post PVE虚拟机UEFI启动时跳转到系统安装界面" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;封面来源： &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.pixiv.net/artworks/102115356&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34; &gt;#背景 空へ - 岡虎次郎/Oka Kojiro的插画 - pixiv&lt;/a&gt;

&lt;span style=&#34;white-space: nowrap;&#34;&gt;&lt;svg width=&#34;.7em&#34; height=&#34;.7em&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 21 21&#34;
        xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;
        &lt;path d=&#34;m13 3l3.293 3.293l-7 7l1.414 1.414l7-7L21 11V3z&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; /&gt;
        &lt;path d=&#34;M19 19H5V5h7l-2-2H5c-1.103 0-2 .897-2 2v14c0 1.103.897 2 2 2h14c1.103 0 2-.897 2-2v-5l-2-2v7z&#34;
            fill=&#34;currentColor&#34;&gt;
    &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;复现&#34;&gt;复现
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;可能是系统安装时未添加EFI磁盘，所以当虚拟机关机重启后，跳转到了系统安装界面
&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419023719image178-1024x487.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1024&#34;
	height=&#34;487&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419023719image178-1024x487_hu_47c93e70b61902a3.png 480w, http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419023719image178-1024x487_hu_209b8cb82a714efd.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;210&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;504px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;检查硬件，发现并无EFI磁盘。
&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419023755image626.png&#34;
	width=&#34;667&#34;
	height=&#34;266&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419023755image626_hu_787cb7723ba91893.png 480w, http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419023755image626_hu_89fe82dc889c47eb.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;250&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;601px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;解决&#34;&gt;解决
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h4 id=&#34;关机&#34;&gt;关机
&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;首先将系统关机，这里我采用强制关机（此虚拟机ID为103，请根据自己情况而定）&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-gdscript3&#34; data-lang=&#34;gdscript3&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;rm &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;lock&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;qemu&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;server&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;lock&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;103.&lt;/span&gt;conf
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;qm stop &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;103&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h4 id=&#34;硬件设置&#34;&gt;硬件设置
&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419025954image197.png&#34;
	width=&#34;293&#34;
	height=&#34;340&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419025954image197_hu_1a76d285bd7e0809.png 480w, http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419025954image197_hu_2da4060426d9989d.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;86&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;206px&#34;
	
&gt;  &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419030005image459.png&#34;
	width=&#34;605&#34;
	height=&#34;234&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419030005image459_hu_e141fb38ffc2b9e8.png 480w, http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419030005image459_hu_dfcb87c593ed0287.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;258&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;620px&#34;
	
&gt;
选择一个存储磁盘即可，其他无需配置。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在设置，引导顺序，只勾选硬盘启动
&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419042607image725.png&#34;
	width=&#34;881&#34;
	height=&#34;500&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419042607image725_hu_3427af1152e6f8ae.png 480w, http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419042607image725_hu_c2ac9bf205dd2274.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;176&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;422px&#34;
	
&gt;
然后启动虚拟机&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;系统配置&#34;&gt;系统配置
&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419042635image613-1024x223.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1024&#34;
	height=&#34;223&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419042635image613-1024x223_hu_957af9f803aade75.png 480w, http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419042635image613-1024x223_hu_ccdbb03c9958752c.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;459&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;1102px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;进入系统后提示这个，等待几秒后出现Shell &lt;br&gt;
输入&lt;code&gt;exit&lt;/code&gt; &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419042724image543.png&#34;
	width=&#34;237&#34;
	height=&#34;83&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419042724image543_hu_56c03d048ede8418.png 480w, http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419042724image543_hu_c5491dd75f3662f.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;285&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;685px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;进入&lt;strong&gt;Device Manager&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419042740image919-1024x720.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1024&#34;
	height=&#34;720&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419042740image919-1024x720_hu_716ed6378e81bc15.png 480w, http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419042740image919-1024x720_hu_ab75c8072dfa8801.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;142&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;341px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;选择&lt;strong&gt;Secure Boot Configuration&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419042819image540-1024x468.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1024&#34;
	height=&#34;468&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419042819image540-1024x468_hu_18585e1fd0989a8.png 480w, http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419042819image540-1024x468_hu_e3064abb2685bbe4.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;218&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;525px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;选中&lt;strong&gt;Attempt Secure Boot&lt;/strong&gt;，点击回车，确保方框内无 &lt;code&gt;X&lt;/code&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419042854image814.png&#34;
	width=&#34;930&#34;
	height=&#34;317&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419042854image814_hu_e1466914b067db1f.png 480w, http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419042854image814_hu_12b76ab96988efdf.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;293&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;704px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这一步为关闭安全启动，后续需要可自行打开&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;连按两次ESC，返回主页面选择Reset
&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419043004image794-1024x652.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1024&#34;
	height=&#34;652&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419043004image794-1024x652_hu_a22869798cee8cf.png 480w, http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419043004image794-1024x652_hu_3617b47fe20f3d1.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;157&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;376px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;重启后在Shell输入&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-fallback&#34; data-lang=&#34;fallback&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;fs0:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;edit startup.nsh
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;然后输入以下内容&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-fallback&#34; data-lang=&#34;fallback&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;\EFI\debian\grubx64.efi
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;我是用debian举例的，其他系统自行替换&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;使用ctrl+s保存，再用ctrl+q退出&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;然后输入reset重启即可&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419043635image310-1024x320.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1024&#34;
	height=&#34;320&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419043635image310-1024x320_hu_44c28897d8d38738.png 480w, http://localhost:1313/p/388/20240419043635image310-1024x320_hu_c62aeb362c3c17ec.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;320&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;768px&#34;
	
&gt;
倒计时结束后将自动进入系统&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
